Package io.tweetninja.cli.Util

Class ConsoleColor

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.tweetninja.cli.Util.ConsoleColor
  • public final class ConsoleColor
extends java.lang.Object
    ConsoleColor is a utility class with static strings that can be put into a console line to add some color. Remember to also use RESET or else the color will persist indefinitely.
